%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: d6fced335fe0e624e8c9d175d9ff6239, type: 3}
  m_Name: OldMan_Dialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  startNodeIndex: 0
  nodes:
  - editorLabel: Old Man - Greeting
    lines:
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: Hm? Who are you? I know every face in this village, and yours isn't one
        of them.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: "Nobody's come in through the roads \u2014 the guards have seen to that.
        And the only other way in is the mountain staircase, which leads to nothing
        but goat trails."
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: ...No, don't tell me. I've lived long enough to know when something strange
        is happening.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices:
    - choiceText: (What do you know about the guards?)
      nextNodeIndex: 1
    - choiceText: (Is there something dangerous nearby?)
      nextNodeIndex: 2
    - choiceText: (I'm just passing through.)
      nextNodeIndex: 3
    nextNodeIndex: -1
  - editorLabel: Old Man - Guards
    lines:
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: Those guards? Useless, the lot of them.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: They showed up a week ago, blocked the eastern road, and have done nothing
        since. Meanwhile, the forest gets worse every day.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: I sit here at my fire and I can hear things moving in the tree line at
        night. Whatever's causing this, it's deep in the forest. South.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: There are caves at the far end, past the great tree. I'd wager that's
        where the source is.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: But nobody listens to an old man. The guards certainly don't.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 4
  - editorLabel: Old Man - The Danger
    lines:
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: "Dangerous? Yes. Something has settled deep in the forest. I can feel
        it in the air \u2014 a wrongness."
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: The animals fled first. Then the monsters came. Small things at first,
        but more every week. They're drawn to something.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: There are caves at the far end of the forest, past the great tree. If
        I were a younger man, I'd go look myself.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: Three hunters already tried. I watched them head south from this very
        spot.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: None of them came back.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 1.5
      tags: []
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: ...A shame, really. They were good people.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 4
  - editorLabel: Old Man - Suspicious
    lines:
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: '''Just passing through.'' Through a village with every exit watched.'
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: You appeared out of nowhere in a place nobody can enter or leave. That's
        not 'passing through,' that's something else entirely.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: ...But you don't look like a threat. You don't look like much of anything,
        really. No offense.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: If you're looking for something to do, the forest to the south could
        use investigating. There are caves at the far end that nobody's been brave
        enough to check.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: Or foolish enough, depending on how you look at it.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 4
  - editorLabel: Old Man - The Push
    lines:
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: You know, you might be exactly what this village needs.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: An outsider. Someone nobody knows. Someone who could go into that forest
        and poke around without drawing attention.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: The villagers are too scared, the guards are too stupid, and I'm too
        old. But you... you've got nothing to lose.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: Head south through the forest, past the great tree with the flowers on
        its trunk. The caves are at the end of the path.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Old Man
      text: I'd keep it quiet, though. No need to worry the others.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: -1
